&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sweat onion with salt, pepper, and plenty of paprika. Remove from heat.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Combine meat, rice, 1 raw egg, and mix thoroughly into the onion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Par-boil peppers, then dry on paper towel.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fill the peppers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1/2 can of sauce in pyrex dish, then put the peppers in the dish, then pour the other 1/2 can on top&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cover tightly with aluminum foil, then bake @ 350 for about 1.5 hours.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
